      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PERFECT STRANGER NZ (6) has put together a string of strong efforts at this circuit and distance including a fighting win last month. Got within 3m of subsequent NSW Derby winner Hollywood Strip when runner-up last start and there are no rivals of that class in this line-up. RICK REILLY NZ (7) has placed in both starts since switching from Victoria to Seaton Grima. Draws wider and makes his first visit to this venue but could have his hoof on the till. LENNETH (3) draws well and can measure up if he shows the form that saw him record back-to-back wins at this circuit and distance earlier in the campaign. QUIET STORM (9) hasn't raced since July but has been readied with a trial and owns a decent record here including a win three back. Market watch.",
